message.body: Hey! Can I get us some dock st take out on Thursday? You're helping me so much - I would love to get you dinner! Or we can meet there at 7 and eat and the go to the studio

Hey!! So nice of you. I'm actually having an early dinner with Alison to get some files from her for class before we meet at 8. Let's do dock street another night! I have a camera for us to do the DV transfer.
